<item>
            <title>[PIG-1513] Pig doesn&apos;t handle empty input directory</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-1513</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>
&lt;p&gt;The following script&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;A = load &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;input&apos;&lt;/span&gt;;
B = load &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;emptydir&apos;&lt;/span&gt;;
C = join B by $0, A by $0 using &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;skewed&apos;&lt;/span&gt;;
store C into &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;output&apos;&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;fails with &quot;ERROR: java.lang.RuntimeException: Empty samples file&apos;;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;In this case, the sample job has 0 maps.  Pig doesn&apos;t expect this and fails . &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;For merge join the script&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The merge join script&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;A = load &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;input&apos;&lt;/span&gt;;
B = load &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;emptydir&apos;&lt;/span&gt;;
C = join A by $0, B by $0 using &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;merge&apos;&lt;/span&gt;;
store C into &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;output&apos;&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;the sample job again has 0 maps and the script  fails with &quot; ERROR 2176: Error processing right input during merge join&quot;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;But if we change the join order: &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;A = load &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;input&apos;&lt;/span&gt;;
B = load &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;emptydir&apos;&lt;/span&gt;;
C = join B by $0, A by $0 using &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;merge&apos;&lt;/span&gt;;
store C into &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;output&apos;&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The second job (merge) now has 0 maps and 0 reduces. And it generates an empty &apos;output&apos; directory.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Order by on empty directory works fine and generates empty part files.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
